byline.original: Correspondence of The New-York Daily Times

lead_paragraph: The Whig State Convention, which assembled at this place yesterday, has just completed its labors, and presented the following very able and excellent ticket: For Governor,....LEONARD J. FARWELL, of Dane co. For Lt. Governor,..JAMES HUGHES, of St. Croix county. For Sec'y of State,.ROBERT W. WRIGHT, of Wrukesha. For At'y-General,..JOHN C. TRUEADELL, of Fond du J,ac. For Treasurer,....JEFFERSON CRAWFORD, of Grant co.
